array.string: Main road begins with the first step.
On the way and father to the son companion.
In game yes in a poputya of people learn.
In dark night the road is far.
To everyone the road.
Where road, there and way.
The way and изъездчив is long.
Sleep at home, and on the way don't doze.
The house thought to the road is no good.
The road even in potholes is better than off road terrain.
The road on which went one thousand years, turns into the river.
The road choose any, and don't forget the native land.
The road will be mastered by the going.
Road people long don't sleep.
Knowing the road isn't tired.
Going the road overcomes, sitting thoughts overcome.
Going any road will master.
What went, such is and arrived.
Who knows the road, that doesn't stumble.
The bad road, than the bad fellow traveler is better.
Persistent will master the road.
Not the long journey learns, and near.
Be not praised by departure, be praised by arrival.
The unfamiliar road is similar to a hole.
Night as day; the road as a cloth - sit down yes slide!
To one to go - and the road is long.
The road is open for open heart.
Peshechk you will be more faithful.
On the bad road far you won't leave.
Direct road - the shortest.
Weak feet get stronger on the way.
I will take a body, and I don't warrant for soul.
Give way to fools and mentally ill people.
What it is fated to find - on the road lies.
Very much to go - to reach not soon.
